snippet.title: Turok: Origins - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Beware, oblivion is at hand! 

Play as the legendary Turok warriors to face off against ferocious dinosaurs and a terrifying alien threat that seeks to destroy all human life in the galaxy. 

Unleash devastating attacks on your enemies with weapons and abilities, and harness fallen enemies’ DNA to upgrade your arsenal. Embark on a high-stakes adventure — solo or with friends — to unravel mysteries that hold the key to saving humanity.

💪 Battle alone or as a team in intense combat.
🏹 Unlock and upgrade advanced weaponry to dominate battles and neutralize your enemies. 
🧬 Extract DNA from fallen foes to unlock game-changing powers that evolve your suit.
📖 Experience an epic story across the Lost Lands.

More information: www.turokorigins.com

Wishlist now:
🖤 Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1967610
💙 PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011183
💚 Xbox Series X|S: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/turok-origins/9NZTBV458RD5
